        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/25444207/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/25444207/" class="">第12页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/wodecuo/" class=" " title="我是小衰">我是小衰</a>
                (总是不自禁的回忆青春年华。)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="25444207">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">有人看这样的书么，我觉得读着好难。真的是在啃书。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-03-28 20:56</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                有人看这样的书么，我觉得读着好难。真的是在啃书。
